content: "When a token is sold, 20% of the proceeds will go towards various systems and programs within the Endgame ecosystem. If a referral code is used, an additional 10% discount will be applied. 3% will be allocated towards the Reward token reflection program, with an additional 1% discount if referred. 14% will go towards liquidity, RFV, Treasury, #Endgame Champion, Algorithmic Chart Management System, and Burning System, with an additional 8% discount if referred. 2% will be allocated towards the Battle Royal Champion System, with an additional 1% discount if referred. Lastly, 1% will go towards the rebaser wallet."
